'''Karl Ameisbichler''' (born 25 March 1927) was an Austrian [[boxing|boxer]]. He competed in the [[Boxing at the 1948 Summer Olympics – Heavyweight|men's heavyweight]] event at the [[1948 Summer Olympics]].<ref name="SportsRef">{{cite Sports-Reference |url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/am/karl-ameisbichler-1.html |title=Karl Ameisbichler Olympic Results |accessdate=13 November 2018}}</ref>

